00044 void CHPQuantificationDetectionFileWriterTest::WriteTest()
00045 {
00046         ParameterNameValueTypeList params;
00047         ParameterNameValueType param;
00048 
00049         CHPQuantificationDetectionData data("CHP_quantification_detection_file");
00050 
00051         data.SetAlgName(L"sig");
00052         data.SetAlgVersion(L"1.0");
00053         data.SetArrayType(L"test3");
00054         data.SetEntryCount(2, 10);
00055 
00056         param.SetName(L"an1");
00057         param.SetValueText(L"av1");
00058         params.push_back(param);
00059         data.AddAlgParams(params);
00060 
00061         params.clear();
00062         param.SetName(L"sn1");
00063         param.SetValueText(L"sv1");
00064         params.push_back(param);
00065         data.AddSummaryParams(params);
00066 
00067 
00068         CHPQuantificationDetectionFileWriter *writer = new CHPQuantificationDetectionFileWriter(data);
00069         affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetQuantificationDetectionData e;
00070 
00071         writer->SeekToDataSet();
00072         e.name = "abc";
00073         e.quantification = 10.0f;
00074     e.pvalue = 0.1f;
00075         writer->WriteEntry(e);
00076         e.name = "xyz";
00077         e.quantification = 20.0f;
00078     e.pvalue = 0.2f;
00079         writer->WriteEntry(e);
00080 
00081         delete writer;
00082 
00083         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(1);
00084 
00085 
00086 
00087 
00088         CHPQuantificationDetectionData data2;
00089         CHPQuantificationDetectionFileReader reader;
00090         reader.SetFilename("CHP_quantification_detection_file");
00091         reader.Read(data2);
00092 
00093         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00094         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00095         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00096         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount() == 2);
00097 
00098         ParameterNameValueTypeList p = data2.GetAlgParams();
00099         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it = p.begin();
00100         param = *it;
00101         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00102         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00103 
00104         p = data2.GetSummaryParams();
00105         it = p.begin();
00106         param = *it;
00107         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00108         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00109 
00110 
00111         data2.GetQuantificationDetectionEntry(0, e);
00112         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.quantification, 10.0f, 0.0001f);
00113         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.pvalue, 0.10f, 0.0001f);
00114         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00115     data2.GetQuantificationDetectionEntry(1, e);
00116         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.quantification, 20.0f, 0.0001f);
00117         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.pvalue, 0.20f, 0.0001f);
00118         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");
00119 
00120 }
